AppZone Community Simulator
======================================
Simulator Powered by the AppZone.lk community

1.0 Introduction
-----------------
This is a SMS Simulator for the Appzone.lk platform and simulate both server and
client as mobile phones

Ultimately This is Java Web project and when build using maven2 you can use with 
any servlet container

2.0 Distribution
-----------------
If you would not like to build your self you can get the binary distribution as well
visit http://bit.ly/appzone-simulator
and soon simulator will be available on the appzone.lk website too

